  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Drain the <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Crumble the <strong>tofu</strong> into a large bowl with your hands with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>soy sauce  </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1646132712839-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1646132712839-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1646132712839-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1646132712839-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1646132712839-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated tofu</strong> to the pan and cook for 6-7 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646132715594-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646132715594-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646132715594-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646132715594-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646132715594-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> lengthways into batons</p><p>Deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646132720449-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646132720449-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646132720449-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646132720449-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646132720449-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until they're fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min until they're tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the noodles and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1646132724297-x200.jpg",
