          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is golden, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>spring onion batons</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
